(57, 28, 'product_s_desc', 'Low temperature fusing and curing, excellent general purpose epoxy coating powder for ceramic, tantalum, and film capacitors.Designed for fluid bed application.Colors available: laser markable gold and a variety of other colors', 'SolEpoxy DK15-02 is a blow-coat brown epoxy coating powder developed for electrical insulation of toroids, current transformers, magnetic and powder cores.\r\n\r\nEpoxy-coated or impregnated magnetic and powder cores can be blow-coated or dipped into a fluidized bed for maximum edge coverage. It offers excellent cut-through temperature resistance with good edge coverage and is UL recognized for 130ºC operating temperature.'),
