(346, 179, 'product_s_desc', 'LINQTAPE PIT0.5-Series is a Kapton HN Film Alternative whose high-temperature resistant polyimide tape is designed for both permanent and temporary bonding in many high temperature applications.  These applications are can be found in semiconductor, smartcard, electronic, automotive and general manufacturing industries.  LINQTAPE PIT0.5S-Series Tape provides an excellent balance of electrical, mechanical, thermal, and chemical properties over a wide range of temperatures.  It can be used in applications that may see temperatures up to 260', 'LINQTAPE PIT0.5-Series is a Kapton HN Film Alternative whose high-temperature resistant polyimide tape is designed for both permanent and temporary bonding in many high temperature applications.  These applications are can be found in semiconductor, smartcard, electronic, automotive and general manufacturing industries.  LINQTAPE PIT0.5S-Series Tape provides an excellent balance of electrical, mechanical, thermal, and chemical properties over a wide range of temperatures.  It can be used in applications that may see temperatures up to 260\r\n\r\n<div class="talkPoint">\r\n<h2>Compare Specialty Tapes and Films</h2>\r\n<p>Specialty tapes and films vary widely in their composition and application. Polyimide tapes are generic versions of DuPont''s Kapton and are high-temperature resistant.  These, like polyester (PET), PTFE (Teflon) and other specialty tapes and films are available in many widths and lengths. Our specialty tape and film selector tool can help you choose the specialty tape or film for your application.</p>\r\n<img src="/images/products/polyimide-tape-polyimide-film.png" />\r\n<div class="clickhere"><a href="/compare/specialty-tapes/">Use Specialty Tape Compare Tool</a></div>\r\n</div>'),
(347, 180, 'product_s_desc', 'LINQTAPE PIT0.5-Series is a Kapton HN Film Alternative whose high-temperature resistant polyimide tape is designed for both permanent and temporary bonding in many high temperature applications.  These applications are can be found in semiconductor, smartcard, electronic, automotive and general manufacturing industries.  LINQTAPE PIT0.5S-Series Tape provides an excellent balance of electrical, mechanical, thermal, and chemical properties over a wide range of temperatures.  It can be used in applications that may see temperatures up to 260\r\n\r\n<div class="talkPoint">\r\n<h2>Compare Specialty Tapes and Films</h2>\r\n<p>Specialty tapes and films vary widely in their composition and application. Polyimide tapes are generic versions of DuPont''s Kapton and are high-temperature resistant.  These, like polyester (PET), PTFE (Teflon) and other specialty tapes and films are available in many widths and lengths. Our specialty tape and film selector tool can help you choose the specialty tape or film for your application.</p>\r\n<img src="/images/products/polyimide-tape-polyimide-film.png" />\r\n<div class="clickhere"><a href="/compare/specialty-tapes/">Use Specialty Tape Compare Tool</a></div>\r\n</div>', 'LINQTAPE PIT0.5-Series is a Kapton HN Film Alternative whose high-temperature resistant polyimide tape is designed for both permanent and temporary bonding in many high temperature applications.  These applications are can be found in semiconductor, smartcard, electronic, automotive and general manufacturing industries.  LINQTAPE PIT0.5S-Series Tape provides an excellent balance of electrical, mechanical, thermal, and chemical properties over a wide range of temperatures.  It can be used in applications that may see temperatures up to 260°C.'),
(348, 181, 'product_s_desc', 'Polyonics has introduced a brand new line of engineered tapes designed for use in and around batteries. The ultra thin, flame retardant Polyonics battery tapes help consumer and industrial battery designers and engineers meet their top priorities of safety, performance, size and weight. The highly engineered tapes provide protection and bonding while isolating batteries. The halogen free, REACH and RoHS flame retardant tapes are available with 13, 25 and 50µm amber or black polyimide films. A variety of adhesives (PSAs) are also available providing total thicknesses as low as 41µm. A variety of liners are offered to suit most die cut and auto application processes. The new line of battery tapes includes optional ESD/antistatic and anti-counterfeit features.', 'CAPLINQ has introduced a brand new line of engineered tapes designed for use in and around batteries. The ultra thin, flame retardant Polyonics battery tapes help consumer and industrial battery designers and engineers meet their top priorities of safety, performance, size and weight. The highly engineered tapes provide protection and bonding while isolating batteries. The halogen free, REACH and RoHS flame retardant tapes are available with 13, 25 and 50µm amber or black polyimide films. A variety of adhesives (PSAs) are also available providing total thicknesses as low as 41µm. A variety of liners are offered to suit most die cut and auto application processes. The new line of battery tapes includes optional ESD/antistatic and anti-counterfeit features.'),
