(359, 190, 'product_s_desc', 'LINQTAPE PIT0.5S-UT-Series describes our Ultra-Thin (0.5mil) Polyimide Tapes with an Ultra-Thin Silicone Adhesive Layer.  PIT0.5S-UT-Series tapes are our thinnest polyimide products to date, with a total thickness of only 1 mil (25µm) yet still has excellent adhesion and mechanical strength at high temperatures.<h3>Ultra-Thin, Flame Retardant Polyimide Tape</h3><p>PIT0.5S-UT-Series Tapes use a polyimide film as a backing material which is the generic version of DuPont''s Kapton HN Film.  This backing is ultra-thin at 0.5mil (13µm) yet is just as flame retardant as its thicker counterparts.  Laminated to this is a pressure sensitive silicone adhesive that also has a 0.5mil (13µm) thickness, allowing that the total thickness of the polyimide film plus adhesive is only 1mil  (25µm) thick.</p><h3>Applications </h3><p>PIT0.5S-UT-Series tapes were developed for anyapplication that needs the mechanical properties of a polyimde film, in its thinnest possible form.  These are often used in electronics applications as well as in batteries.</p>', 'LINQTAPE PIT0.5S-UT-Series describes our Ultra-Thin (0.5mil) Polyimide Tapes with an Ultra-Thin Silicone Adhesive Layer.  PIT0.5S-UT-Series tapes are our thinnest polyimide products to date, with a total thickness of only 1 mil (25µm) yet still has excellent adhesion and mechanical strength at high temperatures.<h2>Ultra-Thin, Flame Retardant Polyimide Tape</h2><p>PIT0.5S-UT-Series Tapes use a polyimide film as a backing material which is the generic version of DuPont''s Kapton HN Film.  This backing is ultra-thin at 0.5mil (13µm) yet is just as flame retardant as its thicker counterparts.  Laminated to this is a pressure sensitive silicone adhesive that also has a 0.5mil (13µm) thickness, allowing that the total thickness of the polyimide film plus adhesive is only 1mil  (25µm) thick.</p><h2>Applications </h2><p>PIT0.5S-UT-Series tapes were developed for anyapplication that needs the mechanical properti