(514, 281, 'product_s_desc', 'LINQTAPE PIT1A-ESD-Black Series is a high-temperature resistant polyimide tape with Electro Static Discharge designed for both permanent and temporary bonding in many high temperature applications.  The PIT1A-ESD Black has the same mechanical properties as our standard PIT1A-Series products, but is black and has a 1µm conductive polymer that provides Electro Static Discharge and makes the tape anti-static.  This product is an alternative to Kapton XC film with an acrylic adhesive layer.', '<p>LINQTAPE PIT1A-ESD-Black Series is a high-temperature resistant polyimide tape with Electro Static Discharge designed for both permanent and temporary bonding in many high temperature applications.  The PIT1A-ESD Black has the same mechanical properties as our standard PIT1A-Series products, but is black and has a 1µm conductive polymer that provides Electro Static Discharge and makes the tape anti-static.</p>\r\n<p>The PIT1A-ESD-Black Series tapes get their conductivity by being carbon-loaded.  As such the film provides both thermal conductivity as well as antistatic control with a surface resistance less than 10E9 ohms per square.  This product is an alternative to Kapton XC film with an acrylic adhesive layer.</p>'),
