(639, 347, 'product_s_desc', '<p>LINQTAPE PIT2S-RL-Series Polyimide Tape is a high-temperature resistant polyimide tape on a 2mil PET Release Liner. It is designed for high temperature temporary bonding applications and it removes cleanly without adhesive residue after exposure to heat or chemicals. It may also be used in electrical insulation applications that require Class H Tape grade.</p>\r\n<h2>LINQTAPE PIT2S-RL-Series Polyimide</h2>\r\n<p></p>', '<p>LINQTAPE PIT2S-RL-Series Polyimide Tape is a high-temperature resistant polyimide tape on a 2mil PET Release Liner. It is designed for high temperature temporary bonding applications and it removes cleanly without adhesive residue after exposure to heat or chemicals. It may also be used in electrical insulation applications that require Class H Tape grade.</p>\r\n<h2>Product Applications</h2>\r\n<p>The 2-mil thickness makes it suitable for applications that require more mechanical strength and breakdown voltage than a standard (1-mil thick) polyimide film.  Having a silicone adhesive also makes it suitable for higher temperature applications than acrylic or rubber.  Finally, being on a liner makes it suitable for applications that require the film to be die-cut.</p>\r\n<h2>APPLICATIONS:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>High Temperature Wafer Dicing Tape</li>\r\n<li>Die-cut polyimide parts</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>PRODUCT FEATURES & BENEFITS:</h2> \r\n<ul><li>2-mil polyimide thickness</li>\r\n<li>Linered</li>\r\n</ul>'),
