(1653, 878, 'product_s_desc', '<p>SolEpoxy™ DK15-0606 Tan is an epoxy based coating powder developed for low and medium voltage (600V - 38,000V) bus bars.  Used for over 20 years by major power distribution companies for low and medium-voltage bus bar applications, DK15-0606 provides a smooth surface appearance with high edge coverage properties and <a href="http://data.ul.com/link/plastics.aspx?PR=PYLNAKMIFDBCPFVRRGVRRROEPQDSCLGR">DK15-0606 is UL recognized</a> for UL94-VO and an RTI of 130ºC operating temperatures. Particle size distribution of DK15-0606 is tailored for application via a fluid bed process.</p>', ''),
